name: FACE TO FACE
description: In the "IN MY SPIRIT" collection, this diptych is the culmination of two previous stages, namely "IN MY SPIRIT" the first part, "Sad Sire" the second part. The two faces of the same face. Which one do I show and which one do I identify with the most? The game of tossing or tossing, with the multiple images of me spinning and spinning again.
